Text: SEC ChampionshipThere is no longer a limit on the number of SEC Championship tickets that you may preorder over the internet If you have any questions please send to mailto your customer number is click on to order tickets The order will only be honored if Auburn defeats LSU on Dec

SEC Championship SEC CHAMPIONSHIP The SEC Championship game will be played at the Georgia Dome in Atlanta on December Since the team representing the western division may not be determined until after the LSUAuburn game on Dec seven days before the Championship Game the SEC office has instructed all teams in contention to begin processing orders at this time Since we are dealing with such a short turn around we have to prepare now as if we are in the game If we do not represent the Western Division your credit card charge will be cancelled If we are in the Championship Game we will be prepared to mail the tickets after December It is imperative that orders are received by the November deadline We will not have the luxury of filling any orders received after November based on priority We will need a street address and daytime phone number because the tickets will be shipped via UPS Next Day Air If you need to change your address or have any questions please send to tomailto Address changes can not be made on the order form You will save when ordering via the internet Your customer number is Click here to order tickets email questions to mailto War Eagle Tim Jackson Director of Athletic Ticket Sales
SEC Tournament TicketsPST Mens SEC Basketball Tournament tickets are now available or call each Lower Level
